as soon as possible.


885
01:21:53.418 --> 01:21:54.586
太好了
Great.


886
01:21:55.253 --> 01:21:56.672
好
Okay.


887
01:21:56.672 --> 01:21:58.048
可以
Yes.


888
01:21:58.048 --> 01:22:00.008
我會在家
I can meet you there.


889
01:22:01.593 --> 01:22:03.011
好
Okay.


890
01:22:03.011 --> 01:22:04.388
謝謝
Thanks.


891
01:22:16.358 --> 01:22:18.819
我先回家，水暖工要來
I have to go meet a plumber.


892
01:22:18.819 --> 01:22:20.570
明天見！
See you tomorrow!


893
01:22:45.679 --> 01:22:47.681
