902
01:23:22.048 --> 01:23:24.634
可能要幾個小時
A few hours, probably.


903
01:23:24.634 --> 01:23:26.511
好，那還是盡快開始吧
All right, well, you better get started.


904
01:23:26.511 --> 01:23:28.511
好
Okay.


905
