他們折磨過我無數次
They tortured me so many times.


913
01:24:34.204 --> 01:24:35.413
有一次
One day...


914
01:24:37.123 --> 01:24:40.585
他們把我的衣服扒光
...they took off all of my clothes,


915
01:24:40.585 --> 01:24:44.464
扔進男牢房…
and threw me into a men's cell


916
01:24:44.464 --> 01:24:46.341
直到天亮
until morning.


917
01:24:58.228 --> 01:25:01.690
你還有什麼想補充的嗎？
Is there anything else you want to add?


918
01:25:02.649 --> 01:25:05.360
我希望用我的真名
I would like to use my real name


919
01:25:05.360 --> 01:25:08.405
增加可信度
to add credibility.


920
01:25:08.405 --> 01:25:10.031
好吧
Okay. All right.I...


921
01:25:11.241 --> 01:25:14.452
我幫你安排了，明天離開中國
I have arranged for you to leave China tomorrow.


922
01:25:15.287 --> 01:25:18.456
不用，我想留下來
No, no, I want to stay.


923
01:25:20.292 --> 01:25:21.626
繼續做我該做的
For change.


924
01:25:21.626 --> 01:25:24.671
真的嗎？太危險了
Are you sure? That's a big risk.


925
01:25:33.179 --> 01:25:35.179
等等

926
