He risked everything for them.


1024
01:38:00.051 --> 01:38:03.763
我真心希望我們也能像他一樣
I only hope we will do the same.


1025
01:38:04.764 --> 01:38:11.520
雖然有些西方國家表達了關切
Now, there have been some concerns raised by Western countries.


1026
01:38:11.520 --> 01:38:17.652
