1027
01:38:18.486 --> 01:38:21.280
我們應該像王博宇那樣
We must be more like Wang.


1028
01:38:21.947 --> 01:38:25.284
盡我們所能
We must do everything we can


1029
01:38:26.619 --> 01:38:28.663
將真相曝光
to bring the truth into the light.


1030
01:38:29.622 --> 01:38:30.665
謝謝！
Thank you!


1031
01:38:32.875 --> 01:38:34.875
謝謝
Thank you.


1032
